Up: Happens when the user presses up arrow, joystick, d-pad.
Down: Happens when the user presses down arrow, joystick, d-pad.
Left: Happens when the user presses left arrow, joystick, d-pad.
Right: Happens when the user presses right arrow, joystick, d-pad.
Next: Happens when the user presses Tab.
Previous: Happens when the user presses Shift+Tab.
